<h3> Research Interests: </h3>
Quantum Internet, Online Machine Learning (e.g., multi-armed bandit, reinforcement learning, etc) and 
Statistical Machine Learning, 
Future Internet Architectures and Protocols, 
Network Science and Economics,
Kernel Support for Large Scale AI Systems.
